g 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pippinbarr.github.io/books/the-stuff-games-are-made-of/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="the-stuff-games-are-made-of-by-pippin-barr"&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Stuff Games Are Made Of&lt;/em&gt; by Pippin Barr&lt;/h2&gt;

